00:24:45,900 --> 00:24:48,060
By understanding that it's dynamic,

687
00:24:48,060 --> 00:24:50,310
by understanding that you
are going to be continually

688
00:24:50,310 --> 00:24:51,360
going in and out

689
00:24:51,360 --> 00:24:55,526
of progressively but
varying levels of focus,

690
00:24:55,526 --> 00:24:58,890
you will greatly release
the pressure on yourself

691
00:24:58,890 --> 00:25:02,160
to feel focused all the
time when you want to be.

692
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:02,993
This is very key.

693
00:25:02,993 --> 00:25:05,520
People who are very good
at focusing understand this

694
00:25:05,520 --> 00:25:09,270
and understand that they
can't expect themselves

695
00:25:09,270 --> 00:25:10,560
to just immediately focus

696
00:25:10,560 --> 00:25:13,050
and then snap into or out of focus.

697
00:25:13,050 --> 00:25:14,640
Okay so be patient with yourself

