00:29:55,230 --> 00:29:57,780
during the actual sets or
during the actual bouts

828
00:29:57,780 --> 00:29:59,190
of running or cycling

829
00:29:59,190 --> 00:30:02,220
or whatever your particular
form of exercise might be.

830
00:30:02,220 --> 00:30:04,350
So deliberate decompression is key.

831
00:30:04,350 --> 00:30:06,780
And I know this is hard because
