832
00:30:06,780 --> 00:30:10,170
by the incredible rich array

833
00:30:10,170 --> 00:30:11,640
of sensory information available

834
00:30:11,640 --> 00:30:13,500
on our phones and other devices,

835
00:30:13,500 --> 00:30:15,390
but I can't emphasize this enough,

836
00:30:15,390 --> 00:30:17,940
our ability to focus is not just related

837
00:30:17,940 --> 00:30:20,820
to what happens during
the entry and movement

838
00:30:20,820 --> 00:30:23,760
through those focused bouts
but after those focused bouts.

839
00:30:23,760 --> 00:30:25,530
We really need to deliberately decompress.

840
00:30:25,530 --> 00:30:27,300
And of course, the ultimate decompress,

841
00:30:27,300 --> 00:30:28,830
the time in which we are not directing

842
00:30:28,830 --> 00:30:30,840
our thinking interaction is during sleep.

843
00:30:30,840 --> 00:30:32,250
And so it's no wonder,

844
00:30:32,250 --> 00:30:34,230
or I should say it holds
