845
00:30:34,230 --> 00:30:37,440
that that deep, long lasting duration

846
00:30:37,440 --> 00:30:39,960
of not controlling where our mind is at

847
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:42,480
is in fact the ultimate
form of restoration,

848
00:30:42,480 --> 00:30:44,310
even if we have very intense dreams.

849
00:30:44,310 --> 00:30:47,730
So take that period after each
90 minute or less focus about,

850
00:30:47,730 --> 00:30:48,840
right, remember those focus bouts

851
00:30:48,840 --> 00:30:50,160
don't have to be full 90 minutes,

852
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:51,870
let's say you do 45 minutes of work,

853
00:30:51,870 --> 00:30:52,703
you're just done with it,

854
00:30:52,703 --> 00:30:55,320
set it down and go do
something for maybe five, 10,

855
00:30:55,320 --> 00:30:58,907
maybe even 30 minutes that
is functional for your day,

856
00:30:58,907 --> 00:31:00,960
right, not just walking around in circles

857
00:31:00,960 --> 00:31:01,860
or staring up at the sky

858
00:31:01,860 --> 00:31:03,690
although if you can do that, do that,

859
00:31:03,690 --> 00:31:05,250
but most of us have other things to do,

860
00:31:05,250 --> 00:31:06,900
but do things that are rather automatic

861
00:31:06,900 --> 00:31:08,040
or reflexive for you,

862
00:31:08,040 --> 00:31:10,440
and try not to do any focused reading,

863
00:31:10,440 --> 00:31:13,260
try not to bring your vision
into a tight location,

864
00:31:13,260 --> 00:31:16,410
such as your phone and try
and deliberately decompress,

865
00:31:16,410 --> 00:31:17,700
because that will allow you

866
00:31:17,700 --> 00:31:20,190
to drop into intense spouts of focus

867
00:31:20,190 --> 00:31:22,620
again repeatedly and
repeatedly throughout the day.

868
00:31:22,620 --> 00:31:25,140
I'm often asked how many ultradian cycles

869
00:31:25,140 --> 00:31:26,760
one can perform throughout the day?

870
00:31:26,760 --> 00:31:28,740
That depends on how well you've slept,

871
00:31:28,740 --> 00:31:29,880
how well you are nourished,

872
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:31,350
which we'll talk about in a moment,

873
00:31:31,350 --> 00:31:34,530
and how well trained up
your focus capacity is.

874
00:31:34,530 --> 00:31:36,714
And here's the paradox,

875
00:31:36,714 --> 00:31:39,540
if you are very trained at focusing,

876
00:31:39,540 --> 00:31:41,610
if you're very good at
dropping into focus,

877
00:31:41,610 --> 00:31:42,780
you're actually going to need

878
00:31:42,780 --> 00:31:44,967
more deliberate decompression and defocus

879
00:31:44,967 --> 00:31:47,400
and I recommend only doing about two,

880
00:31:47,400 --> 00:31:51,090
maybe three deep work sessions per day.

881
00:31:51,090 --> 00:31:54,120
So not one 90 minute session
than expecting yourself

882
00:31:54,120 --> 00:31:55,920
to do to another one and
another one, another one,

883
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:58,350
but rather one deep
work 90 minute session,

884
00:31:58,350 --> 00:32:00,090
and maybe another in the afternoon.

885
00:32:00,090 --> 00:32:01,837
A lot of people get
surprised by this and say,

