per day every single day,

1899
01:09:42,240 --> 01:09:44,520
not just on days where I'm sleep deprived.

1900
01:09:44,520 --> 01:09:45,840
If I happen to be sleep deprived,

1901
01:09:45,840 --> 01:09:49,290
I would extend that NSDR
to 30 or 60 minutes.

1902
01:09:49,290 --> 01:09:50,760
And when you do that NSDR

1903
01:09:50,760 --> 01:09:53,399
will depend on when you
have time for that NSDR.

1904
01:09:53,399 --> 01:09:54,330
When I haven't slept well,

1905
01:09:54,330 --> 01:09:56,340
what I'll try and do is find a quiet place

1906
01:09:56,340 --> 01:09:59,927
where I can do NSDR for
30 or ideally 60 minutes.

1907
01:09:59,927 --> 01:10:02,580
Sometimes I will fall back
asleep during that NSDR,

1908
01:10:02,580 --> 01:10:04,740
that's fine if you do that,

1909
01:10:04,740 --> 01:10:07,484
but most people will stay
awake during the NSDR,

1910
01:10:07,484 --> 01:10:10,260
and then I'll emerge from
that and go about my day.

1911
01:10:10,260 --> 01:10:11,490
If in the afternoon,

1912
